WEBVTT

00:08.905 --> 00:11.708
Every day, you could pass from one continent to the other...

00:11.897 --> 00:13.181
...on a ferry like this one....

00:13.524 --> 00:16.180
...while feeding the seagulls and having a hot cup of tea.

00:16.506 --> 00:18.633
Imagine, if that was your daily commute...

00:18.835 --> 00:20.953
...and you wouldn't even need a passport to do it.

00:27.245 --> 00:29.327
Discover all this and more in Turkey,...

00:29.628 --> 00:31.115
...home of two continents.

